    <section id="mental-health">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Mental Health</h2>
            <h3>What is Mental Health?</h3>
            <p>A state of well-being characterized by optimal functioning, inner equilibrium, and healthy relationships (Bhugra et al., 2013).</p>
            <h3>Importance</h3>
            <p>Helps cope with daily stresses, boosts productivity, and enhances cognitive skills (Fusar-Poli et al., 2019).</p>
            <h3>Challenges</h3>
            <p>Young adults face depression and anxiety, exacerbated during the COVID pandemic (Surgeon General Advisory, 2021).</p>
            <h3>Improvement Tips</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Physical Activity</li>
                <li>Social Connections</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
